# xiaoApple (小苹果)

跨平台，轻量级的阿里云盘同步工具。简单易用。造个轮子自己用...(-_-)


# 安装

```
pip install xiaoApple
```

# 例子

```python


import xiaoApple

localDir = r"c:\users\admin\desktop\syncdir"
aliDir = 'syncdir' 
apple = xiaoApple.Sync(localDir,aliDir)


# 单次同步
apple.run()


# # 自动间隔120秒同步一次
# apple.auto(syncCycleSec=120) 

```

